LatexCommand citet
key "Chow"

\end_inset

.
 Therefore, the 
\begin_inset Formula $E_{v}(\mathbf{k})$
\end_inset

 actually already holds the Coulomb energy of the full valence band.
 The free-carrier calculation implicitly included this energy within the
 band structure result, while it appears here explicitly.
\end_layout

