 & = & \frac{2}{m_{0}\hbar\omega}\left|\left\langle u_{v}\right|\hat{\mathbf{e}}\cdot\mathbf{p}\left|u_{c}\right\rangle \right|^{2}\Omega\,2\left|\varphi_{n}\left(r=0\right)\right|^{2}\delta_{\mathbf{k},0},\end{eqnarray}

\end_inset

where 
